title: MSX Archive Ultimate - 168.8MB Mega ROM Pack - by CAWASAME
description:
In this package you will find the result of years of research and file organization related to MSX files.

To assemble this package, I relied on the most famous collections available on the Internet: "Good Msx"; the TOSEC and "Base Game", in that order!

I developed a special software to identify and remove duplicate files in a more intelligent and insightful way. Whenever there was a conflict, priority was given to "Good MSX", then TOSEC and finally to the "Game based" collection.

Moreover, in this whole package I did not include DSK files. You will find only ROM files in it.

There are 2167 files, making a total of 168.8MB, when unpacked!
